title: We’re Back … With More Experiments!
itunes:title: We’re Back … With More Experiments!
description:
Revisionist History returns on September 15th with a saga about self-sacrifice. Plus, Malcolm offers a mea culpa for an unintended consequence of a chapter he wrote in Outliers.

If you’d like to keep up with the most recent news from this and other Pushkin podcasts, be sure to sign up for our email list at Pushkin.fm.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
